author: breser
msg: Fix the lack of the spacing of messages in the chain of errors in mod_authz_svn.
In particular the default message for an error code would not have been
space separated from other messages and an error with a explicit message
would have had a trailing space if it was the last message.
(log_svn_error): Move the insertion of the space to the top of the loop.
in the prefix passed by the callers to log_svn_error().  log_svn_error()
